liblistserv is a reentrant library to facilitate the communication with a running listserv .  It sends commands to listserv using the TCPGUI interface, and parses the results to provide the C developer with ready to use structures.

Package structure
  /
    AUTHORS          - lists the authors of liblistserv
    ChangeLog        - contains all changes towards previous releases
    configure.ac     - input for autoconf
    COPYING          - license for this package
    Makefile.am      - input for automake
    NEWS             - major changes towars previous releases
    INSTALL          - installation instructions.  Check the documentation for details
    README           - this file
    sieve.mailtpl    - to be appended to site.mailtpl
  /doc               - documentation
  /src               - sources
    content_filter.l - implements listserg_getcontent_filter
    demo.c           - sample progamme using liblistserv
    lcmdx.c          - implements the listserv_command
    liblistserv.c    - implements most exported functions
    liblistserv.h    - declares the exported functions
    list_header.l    - implements listserv_getlist_keyword
    sieve_scripts.c  - implements listserv_getsieve_scripts
